# iRAF Cursor Rules

Read AGENTS.md at the start of every session for full framework reference.
Read CLAUDE.md for build commands and common workflows.

## Non-negotiable rules

- Every entity MUST extend BaseObject and use @iEntity + @iField decorators
- Entity keys: kebab-case plural (e.g. "order-lines")
- Module keys: kebab-case (e.g. "sales")
- Build order when making changes: core → react → plugin-system → modules → app
- Bootstrap order in main.tsx: ModuleRegistry.initAll() → initPlugins() → React render
- @iAction routes are /api/{ControllerClassName}/{methodName} — never use entity key

## Reference files

- Full entity example: modules/sample/src/entities/FeatureGallery.ts
- Master-Detail example: modules/sample/src/entities/MasterItem.ts
- Module definition: modules/sample/src/index.ts
- Field types reference: packages/core/src/types/metadata.ts
